481%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charlie%20Munger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652671f355f52b01b35c340e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharlie%20Munger.%3Cp%3ECNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ECharlie%20Munger%20panned%20crypto%2C%20warned%20about%20AI%20hype%2C%20and%20trumpeted%20Zoom%20at%20Zoomtopia%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20business%20partner%20laid%20out%20some%20of%20the%20best%20methods%20to%20attain%20wealth%20and%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInsider%20spoke%20to%20six%20people%20who%20attended%20Munger's%20closing%20keynote%20at%20the%20private%20event.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECharlie%20Munger%20trashed%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20warned%20the%20AI%20buzz%20seems%20overblown%2C%20and%20praised%20Zoom%20for%20keeping%20him%20connected%20during%20his%20closing%20keynote%20at%20Zoomtopia%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20business%20partner%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbrk-b-stock%5C%22%3EBerkshire%20Hathaway%3C%2Fa%3E's%20vice-chairman%20also%20shared%20some%20of%20his%20best%20tips%20for%20achieving%20success%20in%20business%20and%20life%20at%20the%20private%20event%2C%20including%20hard%20work%2C%20discipline%2C%20saving%2C%20and%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2099-year-old%20investor's%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fzm-stock%5C%22%3EZoom%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Eric%20Yuan%20was%20a%20special%20treat%20for%20in-person%20attendees%20of%20the%20video-conferencing%20company's%20annual%20gathering%2C%20and%20hasn't%20been%20shared%20online%2C%20a%20Zoom%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20to%20six%20people%20who%20were%20in%20the%20room%2C%20and%20Zoom%20confirmed%20their%20recollections%20of%20Munger's%20key%20points%20were%20accurate.%20Here%20are%20their%20comments%2C%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Tobi%20Tungl%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20at%20CTI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20takeaways%20were%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcharlie-munger-buffett-berkshire-musk-tesla-byd-crypto-alibaba-ai-2023-2%5C%22%3Eopinion%20on%20AI%20being%20a%20bit%20overdone%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20market%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fcharlie-munger-crypto-ban-bitcoin-regulation-gambling-buffett-berkshire-china-2023-2%5C%22%3Ehis%20opinion%20that%20crypto%20was%20never%20anything%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Memory%20serves%20me%20that%20he%20said%20'overly%20hyped'%20or%20similar.%20He%20had%20some%20stories%20on%20how%20AI%20has%20been%20around%20for%20over%2050%20years%2C%20but%20we%20are%20just%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20surface%20as%20of%20late.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Craig%20Durr%2C%20research%20director%20at%20The%20Futurum%20Group%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMunger%20shared%20his%20seasoned%20perspective%20on%20crypto%20and%20AI%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20which%20he%20was%20skeptical%20about.%20Yet%2C%20with%20nearly%20a%20century%20of%20wisdom%20and%20a%20financial%20track%20record%20to%20match%2C%20his%20views%20command%20respect.%20Eric%20Yuen%20chose%20to%20acknowledge%20rather%20than%20dispute.%20After%20all%2C%20when%20a%20legend%20speaks%2C%20the%20room%20listens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Mark%20Friedler%2C%20CEO%20of%20Gigex%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMunger%20had%20a%20wry%20and%20great%20sense%20of%20humor.%20He%20was%20super%20negative%20about%20crypto%20and%20called%20it%20a%20scam.%20He%20said%20communications%20help%20drive%20business%2C%20and%20business%20success%20is%20about%20focus%20and%20consistency.%20Like%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20he%20didn't%20see%20large%20success%20until%20later%20in%20life%2C%20and%20only%20massive%20success%20after%20his%2060s.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Eric%20Kunnen%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20IT%20innovation%20and%20research%20at%20Grand%20Valley%20State%20University%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fzoom-eric-yuan-charlie-munger-warren-buffett-video-tech-support-2021-8%5C%22%3ECharlie%20loves%20Zoom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20uses%20it%20frequently%20for%20business%20and%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20family%2C%20as%20it's%20difficult%20for%20him%20to%20travel.%20His%20business%20advice%20was%20to%20build%20a%20better%20product%20or%20offer%20a%20better%20solution%2C%20that%20it's%20all%20about%20competition%2C%20and%20that%20successful%20people%20are%20those%20with%20the%20acumen%20to%20understand%20life%20better%20than%20everyone%20else.%20He%20said%20it's%20up%20to%20you%20to%20work%20harder%20and%20better%20than%20the%20next%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharlie%20also%20said%20investments%20are%20better%20than%20money%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20go%20to%20the%20office%20to%20work%20in%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Melody%20Brue%2C%20VP%20and%20principal%20tech%20analyst%20at%20Moor%20Insights%20%26amp%3B%20Strategy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20my%20biggest%20takeaway%20%E2%80%94%20and%20probably%20a%20big%20reason%20for%20having%20him%20%E2%80%94%20was%20that%20Charlie%20stays%20connected%20to%20people%20through%20Zoom%20at%2099%20when%20he%20doesn't%20get%20out%20as%20much%20as%20he%20once%20did.%20There%20are%20physical%20limitations%20at%20that%20age%20and%20Zoom%20has%20kept%20him%20engaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharlie%20spoke%20about%20working%20to%20get%20ahead.%20He%20said%20to%20'spend%20less%20than%20you%20make%2C'%20and%20invest%20the%20money%20you%20save.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20had%20a%20plate%20of%20donuts%20with%20him%20on%20stage%2C%20and%20Charlie%20made%20the%20point%20that%20donuts%20aren't%20good%20for%20you%2C%20but%20you%20can%20have%20them%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20disciplined%20though%2C%20and%20know%20that%20you%20can%20only%20have%20so%20much%20for%20it%20to%20not%20be%20bad%20for%20you.%20It%20was%20cute%20and%20it%20illustrated%20Charlie's%20mental%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharlie%20also%20talked%20a%20lot%20about%20poker%20and%20trust.%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20was%20necessarily%20saying%20you%20can't%20trust%20people%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20caution%20about%20people's%20motives%20in%20business%2C%20and%20how%20you%20have%20to%20be%20good%20at%20reading%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20be%20a%20good%20'poker%20player'%20yourself%20when%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20very%20funny%20and%20the%20conversation%20between%20him%20and%20Eric%20felt%20like%20watching%20old%20friends%20catch%20up%20-%20not%20a%20typical%20'celebrity'%20keynote%20that%20are%20pretty%20much%20all%20the%20same.%20They%20gave%20away%20a%20copy%20of%20Charlie's%20book%20upon%20exit.%20The%20books%20were%20gone%20in%20seconds!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20David%20Maldow%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Let's%20Do%20Video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCharlie%20had%20a%20few%20good%20jokes%20about%20his%20age.%20I%20think%20he%20used%20the%20old%20standby%20about%20how%20'it's%20great%20to%20be%20anywhere'%20at%20the%20start.%20He%20is%2099%2C%20but%20his%20thoughts%20were%20all%20coherent%20and%20he%20is%20charming%20and%20funny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20few%20moments%20where%20Eric%20was%20asking%20about%20taking%20risks%2C%20and%20seemed%20to%20expect%20Charlie%20to%20encourage%20risk%20taking%2C%20but%20Charlie%20seemed%20risk%20avoidant.%20He%20gave%20the%20impression%20that%20he%20didn't%20get%20rich%20from%20wild%2C%20risky%20investments%2C%20but%20from%20not%20being%20stupid.%20Basic%2C%20smart%20investments%20and%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20even%20brought%20up%20the%20topic%20of%20poker%20as%20part%20of%20the%20risk%20discussion.%20Eric%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20Charlie%20would%20play%20poker%20with%20a%20cheater%20at%20the%20table.%20Charlie's%20answer%20was%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20play%20poker%20with%20that%20person%2C%20and%20he%20only%20plays%20poker%20with%20people%20that%20he%20can%20beat.%20The%20implication%20was%20that%20was%20how%20he%20wins%20at%20business%20at%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%2C%20heartwarming%20moment%20was%20when%20he%20explained%20how%20his%20entire%20family%20does%20big%20Zoom%20meetings%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20very%20big%20deal%20for%20him%20because%20traveling%20is%20too%20hard%20for%20him%20now%20due%20to%20the%20wheelchair.%20He%20said%20that%20being%20able%20to%20see%20them%20all%2C%20despite%20his%20failing%20eyesight%2C%20meant%20so%20much%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-munger-zoomtopia-keynote-buffett-berkshire-crypto-ai-bitcoin-investing-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697022212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F620e2057462ff20019c56e68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcharlie-munger-zoomtopia-keynote-buffett-berkshire-crypto-ai-bitcoin-investing-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett's%20business%20partner%20said%20he's%20skeptical%20of%20crypto%20and%20AI%2C%20and%20shared%20tips%20on%20attaining%20wealth%20and%20success%2C%20during%20his%20Zoomtopia%20keynote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcharlie-munger-zoomtopia-keynote-buffett-berkshire-crypto-ai-bitcoin-investing-2023-10%22%