.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F31135906%2F15010336808_383bd10b55_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20August%2017%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Union%20coal%20ministry%20declared%20the%20Adani%20Group%20as%20the%20successful%20bidder%20for%20a%20250%20million%20tonne%20coal%20block%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Singrauli%20forests.%20The%20auction%20for%20the%20Gondbahera%20Ujheni%20East%20coal%20block%20was%20unusual.%20Adani%20Group%20was%20the%20lone%20bidder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDocuments%20reviewed%20by%3Cem%3E%C2%A0The%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eshow%20the%20Adani%20group%20cornered%20the%20block%20even%20when%20the%20auction%20failed%20because%20the%C2%A0%20government%20had%20quietly%20changed%20the%20coal%20auction%20rules%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20companies%20to%20grab%20coal%20blocks%20even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20reveal%20that%20the%20government%20has%20given%20itself%20the%20discretionary%20powers%20to%20allot%20coal%20blocks%20to%20lone%20bidders%20even%20when%20auctions%20fail%20to%20deliver%20competitive%20bids.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20also%20contradict%20the%20assertive%20claims%20of%20transparency%20made%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20amid%20much%20hype%2C%20introduced%20new%20laws%20and%20regulations%20to%20auction%20coal%20blocks.%20Seven%20years%20later%20the%20promise%20of%20ending%20discretionary%20allocation%20and%20replacing%20it%20with%20fair%20competition%20are%20tossed%20aside%20when%20auctions%20fail.These%20rules%20have%20also%20undermined%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20landmark%202014%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20that%20struck%20down%20arbitrary%20and%20discretionary%20allocations%20of%20coal%20blocks%2C%20an%20order%20that%20annulled%20204%20such%20allocations%20by%20the%20previous%20UPA%20government%20that%20were%20dubbed%20by%20the%20media%20as%20%E2%80%98Coalgate%20scam%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecords%20show%20the%20Adani%20group%20is%20not%20the%20only%20beneficiary%20of%20these%20discretionary%20powers%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20handed%20itself.%20The%C2%A0%20government%20has%20resorted%20to%20such%20discretion%20in%20at%20least%2012%20cases%20and%20allocated%20coal%20blocks%20to%20private%20companies%20after%20failing%20to%20attract%20competition.%20The%20firms%20that%20have%20bagged%20these%20blocks%20include%20Vedanta-owned%20firms%2C%20JSW%20Steel%2C%20Birla%20Corporation%20and%20other%20lesser-known%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Ftrc%2Fcoal-forests-part-1%5C%22%3Epart%20one%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20investigative%20series%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Collective%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Erevealed%20how%20the%20power%20industry%20lobby%20got%20the%20government%20to%20open%20up%20sensitive%20forest%20patches%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20coal%20mining.%20The%20lobby%20eyed%20two%20blocks%20in%20particular.%20Adani%20Group%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20lobby%2C%20was%20the%20lone%20bidder%20for%20one%20of%20the%20two%20blocks%20the%20government%20opened%20up%20after%20overturning%20years%20of%20advice%20from%20the%20environment%20ministry%20against%20such%20a%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPart%20two%20of%20the%20series%20reveals%20how%20the%20government%20gives%20away%20coal%20blocks%20to%20private%20companies%20through%20a%20discretionary%20government%20allotment%20route%20when%20only%20a%20single%20bidder%20turns%20up%20for%20the%20auctions.%20The%20fire%20sale%20of%20coal%20mines%20comes%20despite%20the%20country%20not%20needing%20additional%20coal%20supply%20now%2C%20and%20having%20allocated%20enough%20coal%20blocks%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20power%20requirements%20for%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20report%20was%20originally%20published%20by%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%3Cem%