E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20interview%20with%20a%2030-year-old%20financial%20dominatrix%20who%20uses%20the%20name%20Hope%20Vicious.%20Her%20sources%20of%20income%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2018%20and%20living%20on%20my%20own%20in%20Maryland%20in%20a%20superexpensive%20apartment%2C%20I%20started%20using%20a%20webcam%20to%20sell%20sexual%20content%20to%20pay%20the%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20this%20for%20about%20two%20years%20but%20didn't%20like%20it%20that%20much.%20I%20researched%20other%20kinks%20and%20found%20financial%20domination%2C%20which%20sounded%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20dominating%20people%20financially.%20People%20I%20connect%20with%20on%20kink%20sites%20or%20on%20regular%20social-media%20sites%20such%20as%20Twitter%20will%20send%20me%20money%2C%20through%20an%20app%20like%20CashApp%2C%20either%20for%20no%20reason%20at%20all%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20some%20attention%2C%20or%20for%20a%20specific%20request.%20It's%20often%20online%20but%20sometimes%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20I%20dominate%20are%20mostly%20men%2C%20but%20there%20are%20sometimes%20women%20and%20nonbinary%20people.%20Often%20they%20are%20people%20in%20positions%20of%20power%20%E2%80%94%20a%20CEO%2C%20a%20boss%2C%20or%20a%20breadwinner%20of%20a%20family%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20want%20to%20submit%20to%20me%20in%20the%20form%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20decided%20I%20wanted%20to%20put%20myself%20out%20there%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20with%20being%20dominant.%20Before%20putting%20myself%20out%20there%2C%20I%20did%20months%20of%20research.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20information%20out%20there%20%E2%80%94%20articles%2C%20educational%20websites%2C%20YouTube%20videos.%20Then%20there%20are%20women%20who%20teach%20classes%20or%20offer%20guides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20I%20made%20a%20Twitter%2C%20now%20X%2C%20account%20and%20started%20advertising%20myself%20as%20a%20financial%20dominatrix.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20reached%20out.%20Many%20were%20time%20wasters%20who%20didn't%20end%20up%20sending%20money%2C%20but%20within%20my%20first%20month%2C%20I%20was%20making%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20wasters%20often%20make%20bait%20posts%20along%20the%20lines%20of%3A%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20just%20can't%20find%20a%20findomme%20to%20serve%20anywhere!%26quot%3B%20Then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20about%2050%20women%20will%20reply%20to%20them%20saying%20that%20they%20can%20approach%20them.%20But%20then%20they%20get%20all%20this%20free%20attention%20with%20no%20real%20intention%20of%20sending%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20my%20findomme%20business%20works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20send%20money%20because%20they%20want%20to%20be%20humiliated%20or%20ignored%2C%20or%20I'll%20do%20a%20session%20with%20them.%20This%20can%20mean%20a%20bunch%20of%20different%20things%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20that%20falls%20under%20the%20domination%20umbrella%20can%20be%20a%20findomme-type%20session%2C%20such%20as%20humiliation%20or%20foot-worship%20sessions%20combined%20with%20them%20sending%20me%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20subs%2C%20I'll%20be%20sent%20money%2C%20and%20I'll%20acknowledge%20that%20they%20sent%20it%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20go%20past%20that.%20Some%20financial%20submissives%20don't%20expect%20acknowledgment%20or%20anything%20%E2%80%94%20they%20get%20a%20rush%20from%20sending%20the%20money%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20thing%20called%20%26quot%3Bdrains%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20they'll%20send%20you%20money%20over%20and%20over%20while%20you%20maybe%20chat%20for%20a%20little%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20get%20super%20explicit%3B%20I%20don't%20do%20any%20nudity.%20I%20do%20censored%20content%2C%20where%20I%20pose%20in%20a%20photo%20but%20my%20whole%20body%20is%20pixelated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20fine%20with%20clients%20being%20nude%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20speak%20with%20me%20sexually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20to%20meet%20subs%20in%20person%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20sub%20I%20met%20in%20person%20was%20someone%20who%20lived%2020%20minutes%20from%20me.%20I%20was%20very%20nervous%20as%20I%20was%20still%20learning%20the%20ropes.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20to%20say%20or%20how%20to%20act.%20Even%20when%20you%20do%20the%20research%2C%20it's%20a%20big%20jump%20from%20just%20having%20to%20say%20thank%20you%20online%20to%20meeting%20someone%20in%20person%20to%20%26quot%3Bdominate%26quot%3B%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20followed%20me%20around%20the%20mall%20carrying%20all%20the%20bags%20and%20swiping%20his%20card%20in%20the%20stores%2C%20while%20I%20essentially%20made%20fun%20of%20him.%20He%20bought%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes%20for%20my%20boyfriend%20at%20the%20time%2C%20some%20clothes%20for%20me%2C%20and%20video%20games%20for%20both%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0totaling%20about%20%24250.%20He%20then%20took%20out%20%24150%20at%20an%20ATM%20and%20gave%20it%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20with%20that%20boyfriend%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20he%20was%20fine%20with%20what%20I%20did.%20I've%20been%20with%20my%20current%20partner%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20he's%20equally%20OK%20with%20it.%20Communication%20is%20key%20to%20keeping%20everyone%20involved%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20boyfriend%20doesn't%20typically%20participate%2C%20some%20of%20my%20subs%20will%20send%20him%20money%2C%20and%20sometimes%20he'll%20come%20along%20to%20an%20in-person%20session%20for%20my%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%26quot%3Bowned%20sub%26quot%3B%20is%20someone%20who%20wants%20to%20serve%20one%20domme%20and%20not%20serve%20anybody%20else.%20It's%20a%20lot%20more%20intimate%20%E2%80%94%20you%20get%20to%20dive%20deeper%20into%20what%20they%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20up%20to%20seven%20owned%20subs%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20require%20them%20to%20send%20me%20%24100%20a%20week%20on%20a%20set%20day%2C%20but%20then%20I%20expect%20them%20to%20be%20consistently%20sending%20more%20than%20that%20through%20CashApp%20or%20buying%20me%20things%20on%20my%20Amazon%20wish%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20I%20demand%20%24400%20a%20month%20from%20them%20but%20expect%20about%20%241%2C500.%20If%20I%20had%20an%20owned%20sub%20that%20wasn't%20consistently%20hitting%20that%2C%20I'd%20warn%20them.%20If%20they%20kept%20missing%20that%20figure%2C%20I'd%20have%20to%20tell%20them%20that%20it's%20not%20working%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20love%20my%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20being%20a%20findomme.%20It's%20exhilarating%20and%20a%20massive%20confidence%20boost.%20I'm%20essentially%20paid%20to%20live%20a%20life%20of%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20fund%20my%20hobbies%20of%20gaming%2C%20music%2C%20and%20art.%20I%20can%20spend%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20on%20collecting%20Magic%3A%20The%20Gathering%20cards%20and%20%24500%20a%20month%20on%20%26quot%3BFortnite%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20go%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20exceptionally%20luxurious%20taste.%20I%20don't%20buy%20limited%20designer%20and%20high-end%20brands.%20That%20said%2C%20I'm%20looking%20to%20treat%20myself%20to%20a%20Rolex%20for%20Christmas%20and%20another%20BMW%20for%20my%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-dominatrix-what-its-like-owned-subs-send-money-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697018711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6523daf068f1d46f52ab7e9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-dominatrix-what-its-like-owned-subs-send-money-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hope%20Vis