syBggCEEUYOzIGCAMQRRg7MgYIBBBFGDsyBggFEEUYPDIGCAYQRRg8MgYIBxBFGD3SAQgxNDczajBqN6gCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%26bshm%3Drime%2F1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworking%20multiple%20remote%20jobs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20boost%20their%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%205%25%20of%20workers%20in%20a%20typical%20organization%20have%20two%20full-time%20jobs%20concurrently%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20McKinsey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Fcapabilities%2Fpeople-and-organizational-performance%2Four-insights%2Fsome-employees-are-destroying-value-others-are-building-it-do-you-know-the-difference%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereport%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20surveyed%20over%2015%2C000%20workers%20across%20seven%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20between%20last%20November%20and%20January.%20McKinsey%20called%20the%20trend%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20phenomenon%26quot%3B%20that's%20been%20driven%2C%20in%20part%2C%20by%20more%20remote%20workers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-works-two-remote-jobs-great-resignation-inflation-rent-tuition-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etaking%20on%20a%20second%20remote%20job%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20likely%20without%20their%20employer's%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20say%20these%20workers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-viral-linkedin-post-engineers-working-two-jobs-overemployment-theft-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeating%20their%20employers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20providing%20more%20fuel%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-working-model-wfh-work-from-home-policy-office-trends-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Proponents%20say%20the%20trend%20is%20a%20symptom%20of%20broader%20problems%20in%20the%20US%2C%20like%20low%20wages%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-college-housing-healthcare-childcare-more-affordable-abundance-agenda-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20it's%20not%20an%20issue%20as%20long%20as%20workers'%20job%20performance%20remains%20strong.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWorkplace%20experts%20told%20Insider%20that%20as%20long%20as%20workers%20are%20successfully%20juggling%20both%20jobs%2C%20their%20bosses%20should%20consider%20cutting%20them%20some%20slack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20double-dipping%20jobs%20can%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecond-jobs-secret-salary-income-money-remote-work-overemployed-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20a%20worker's%20finances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20trend%20is%20also%20contributing%20to%20an%20increase%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Btime%20theft%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20being%20paid%20to%20work%20for%20one%20company%20when%20really%20doing%20work%20for%20another%2C%20said%20David%20Barron%2C%20a%20Texas-based%20labor%20and%20employment%20attorney%20with%20the%20law%20firm%20Cozen%20O'Connor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20problem%20exploded%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20working%20from%20home%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20flexibility%20allowed%20by%20many%20employers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concern%20is%20employees%20diverting%20time%20and%20resources%20away%20from%20their%20primary%20employer%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20another%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarron%20said%20that%20most%20workers%20don't%20have%20employment%20agreements%20that%20explicitly%20prohibit%20them%20from%20working%20second%20jobs.%20But%20holding%20two%20remote%20jobs%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-3-full-time-remote-jobs-makes-344k-pay-mortgage-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebreach%20some%20employment%20contracts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20lead%20to%20job%20termination.%20It's%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fequifax-fires-employees-for-working-two-jobs-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehappened%20to%20some%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who've%20been%20found%20out%2C%20including%20at%20least%20two%20dozen%20at%20the%20credit-reporting%20giant%20Equifax%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20jobs%20may%20not%20be%20a%20problem%20unless%20an%20employee's%20work%20suffers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20employers%20expect%20their%20workers%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20their%20jobs%20for%2040-plus%20hours%20per%20week%2C%20Aaron%20De%20Smet%2C%20a%20McKinsey%20senior%20partner%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20a%20co-author%20of%20the%20report%2C%20told%20Insider.%20But%20bosses%20should%20be%20more%20focused%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20work%20rather%20than%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20employees%20put%20in%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20have%20found%20ways%20to%20get%20all%20the%20work%20done%20in%2020%20to%2030%20hours%20rather%20than%2040%2C%20and%20don't%20mind%20working%2040-%20to%2060-hour%20weeks%20across%20two%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20an%20employer%20needs%20to%20own%20more%20of%20their%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Moss%2C%20a%20workplace%20culture%20expert%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Burnout%20Epidemic%2C%26quot%3B%20echoed%20De%20Smet%20and%20said%20that%20side%20hustles%20only%20become%20a%20problem%20when%20workers%20aren't%20meeting%20their%20goals.%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EAs%20long%20as%20those%20objectives%20are%20being%20met%2C%20then%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20ourselves%2C%20'Does%20it%20really%20matter%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20one%20Gen%20Xer%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20was%20able%20to%20squeeze%20the%20work%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-3-full-time-remote-jobs-makes-344k-pay-mortgage-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20full-time%20remote%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20roughly%2040%20hours%20per%20week.%20As%20of%20May%2C%20he%20was%20earning%20%24344%2C000%20per%20year%20from%20his%20combined%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDe%20Smet%20said%20that%20working%20longer%20hours%20doesn't%20always%20result%20in%20more%20productivity%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20employees%2C%20when%20forced%20to%20work%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20just%20take%20more%20time%20to%20do%20the%20same%20work%2C%20or%20use%20the%20extra%20time%20to%20send%20unnecessary%20emails%2C%20join%20meetings%20unnecessarily%2C%20get%20involved%20in%20others'%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompanies%20should%20ask%20why%20their%20workers%20are%20double-dipping%20if%20it%20becomes%20a%20problem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20double-dipping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2023-10-09%2Ftwo-full-time-jobs-that-s-a-remote-work-myth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremains%20rare%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20share%20of%20multiple%20jobholders%20in%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FLNU02026631%230%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eisn't%20considerably%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20historical%20norms.%20But%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit%20could%20become%20more%20popular%20as%20the%20remote%20work%20revolution%20provides%20additional%20opportunities%20for%20Americans%20to%20take%20on%20more%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20employee%20with%20multiple%20jobs%20is%20unable%20to%20give%20the%20extra%20attention%20or%20effort%20necessary%20to%20their%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emain%20role%2C%20this%20becomes%20a%20problem%20for%20businesses%2C%20De%20Smet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20some%20companies%20have%20tightened%20their%20policies%20and%20included%20additional%20disclosure%20and%20approval%20requirements%20to%20discourage%20double-dipping%2C%20Barron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20tweaking%20policies%2C%20Moss%20said%20that%20employers%20should%20consider%20what%20is%20driving%20their%20employees%20to%20seek%20out%20another%20job%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20low%20pay%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20meaningful%20work%2C%20or%20too%20much%20time%20on%20their%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20that%20workload%20is%20manageable%20%E2%80%94%20we%20don't%20want%20workers%20burned%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20underwork%20can%20be%20soul-sucking.%20If%20we've%20built%20up%20our%20skills%20and%20they're%20not%20being%20utilized%2C%20we'll%20seek%20out%20new%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20should%20scrutinize%20workers'%20responsibilities%20to%20ensure%20they%20stay%20busy%2C%20Nicole%20Coomber%2C%20a%20clinical%20professor%20in%20management%20%26amp%3B%20organization%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20if%20people%20can%20work%20multiple%20jobs%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20then%20I%20need%20to%20redefine%20their%20role%20to%20be%20more%20rigorous%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20double-dippers%20may%20be%20trying%20to%20simply%20cheat%20their%20employers%2C%20De%20Smet%20said%20businesses%20shouldn't%20be%20too%20quick%20to%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20employees%20are%20not%20violating%20their%20employment%20contract%2C%20bosses%20should%20treat%20these%20employees%20with%20an%20open%20mind%20and%20avoid%20treating%20them%20as%20inherently%20bad%20or%20toxic%20members%20of%20the%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20number%20of%20them%20may%20be%20double%20dipping%20out%20of%20necessity%20%E2%80%94%20their%20salaries%20are%20not%20sufficient%20to%20support%20their%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20working%20multiple%20remote%20jobs%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20willing%20to%20discuss%20details%20about%20your%20pay%20and%20schedule%3F%20If%20so%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoonlighting-working-two-remote-jobs-legal-financial-freedom-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697018462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525b09255f52b01b35b967b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoonlighting-working-two-remote-jobs-legal-financial-freedom-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remote%20workers%20secretly%20holding%20two%20jobs%20aren't%20always%20the%20problem%2C%20experts%20say.%20Companies%20should%20ask%20themselves%20why%20their%20employees%20are%20double-dipping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoonlighting-working-two-remote-jobs-legal-financial-freedom-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20Delimitation%20Over%2C%202%20Voter%20Revisions%20Done%2C%20But%20Elections%20Nowhere%20in%20Sight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F04125435%2Fsrinagar-23681285132975Y7qv.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20continues%20to%20be%20under%20direct%20central%20rule%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20come%20under%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20major%20political%20forces%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20delay%E2%80%9D%20in%20restoration%20of%20an%20assembly%20in%20the%20union%20territory.%20Major%20decisions%20affecting%201.3%20crore%20people%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20are%20instead%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20and%20bureaucrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20has%20faced%20fresh%20brickbats%20after%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20on%20Monday%20(October%209)%20said%20that%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20polls%20would%20be%20announced%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20time%E2%80%9D%20after%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20security%20situation%20and%20other%20polls%20due%20in%20the%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EECI%20faces%20criticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20repetition%20of%20his%20two%20earlier%20statements%20on%20conducting%20polls%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20the%20CEC%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20polls%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20time%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20the%20security%20situation%20and%20other%20simultaneous%20elections%20due%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20statement%20has%20come%20under%20widespread%20criticism%20from%20political%20parties%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20and%20National%20Conference%20vice-president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20asked%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20to%20tell%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20why%20they%20are%20being%20denied%20of%20their%20democratic%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20ask%20him%20(CEC)%20what%20are%20the%20factors%20(for%20not%20holding%20elections)%3F%20We%20feel%20that%20there%20is%20only%20one%20factor%20and%20that%20is%20the%20fear%20factor%20for%20BJP.%20BJP%20was%20earlier%20hiding%20behind%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20now%20they%20are%20hiding%20behind%20the%20ECI%2C%E2%80%9D%20Omar%20said%20during%20a%20news%20conference%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20ECI%2C%20instead%20of%20taking%20its%20decisions%20independently%2C%20is%20working%20on%20directives%20from%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CHas%20the%20situation%20worsened%20so%20much%20that%20you%20(ECI)%20cannot%20hold%20polls%3F%20If%20the%20situation%20has%20deteriorated%20to%20that%20extent%20then%20tell%20us.%20Till%20now%20the%20entire%20world%20has%20been%20told%20that%20the%20situation%20has%20improved%20considerably%20after%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20Omar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20opposition%20parties%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20Congress%20and%20PDP%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20staged%20a%20joint%20sit-in%20at%20Jammu%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20democratic%20rights%20in%20the%20union%20territory.%20The%20parties%20had%20announced%20the%20protest%20programme%20on%20October%203%20during%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20NC%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20to%20discuss%20the%20current%20political%20situation%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20NC%20leader%20and%20MP%20from%20Anantnag%2C%20Justice%20(retd)%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20said%20the%20ECI%20has%20failed%20to%20perform%20its%20constitutional%20obligation%20of%20reviving%20democratic%20processes%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20democracy%2C%20everything%20hinges%20on%20elections%20but%20no%20elections%20have%20taken%20places%20here%20for%20so%20many%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20poll%20body%20has%20no%20reason%20to%20delay%20the%20elections%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20itself%20claims%20that%20the%20security%20situation%20has%20improved%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20PDP%20leader%20and%20former%20minister%20Naeem%20Akther%20said%20the%20ECI%20has%20now%20become%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccompromised%E2%80%9D%20institution%20like%20other%20government%20agencies%20and%20departments.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20past%20that%20they%20have%20kept%20considerations%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20mind%20rather%20than%20the%20constitutional%20requirements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkther%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20scared%20to%20hold%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20does%20experiments%20only%20to%20get%20results%20of%20its%20choice.%20Half%20of%20the%20work%20was%20done%20by%20the%20party%20through%20delimitation%20but%20even%20that%20work%20is%20now%20slipping%20out%20of%20its%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20scared%20to%20hold%20local%20body%20polls%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20adverse%20outcome%20in%20Jammu%20Municipal%20Corporation%20would%20have%20a%20fallout%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20other%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJammu%20is%20considered%20as%20a%20bellwether%20for%20North%20India.%20It%20(an%20adverse%20outcome%20for%20the%20BJP)%20will%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20entire%20India%20that%20sentiment%20is%20against%20the%20BJP.%20It%20will%20also%20impact%20the%20other%20states%20that%20are%20going%20to%20polls.%20The%20debacle%20would%20also%20be%20a%20resounding%20defeat%20of%20their%20propaganda%20on%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20polls%20has%20also%20raised%20questions%20from%20different%20non-political%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERadha%20Kumar%2C%20a%20former%20interlocutor%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20credibility%20has%20come%20into%20question%20over%20the%20inordinate%20delay%20in%20holding%20the%20assembly%20elections%20.%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20sad%20to%20say%20that%20all%20their%20actions%20from%20delimitation%20commission%20to%20now%2C%20indicate%20that%20it%20has%20no%20credibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumar%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20hold%20talks%20with%20different%20shades%20of%20opinion%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20the%202010%20unrest%2C%20said%20that%20the%20delay%20in%20polls%20was%20%E2%80%9Cappalling%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cincomprehensible%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20says%20that%20they%20have%20a%20control%20over%20violence%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20doing%20economically%20well%2C%20but%20then%20why%20they%20are%20not%20holding%20the%20elections%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECEC%E2%80%99s%20three%20statements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20third%20time%20in%202023%20when%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20that%20elections%20would%20be%20held%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20taking%20into%20considerations%20different%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2018%2C%202023%2C%20Kumar%20said%20that%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20will%20be%20held%20after%20taking%20weather%2C%20security%20concerns%20and%20schedule%20of%20elections%20in%20other%20states%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20on%20March%2028%2C%202023%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20chief%20said%20that%20the%20commission%20is%20aware%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvacuum%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20filled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20said%20the%20fresh%20revision%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20does%20not%20disturb%20schedule%20or%20conduct%20part%20of%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20scheduled%20part%2C%20the%20conduct%20part%20that%20depends%20on%20various%20other%20factors%20which%20we%20will%20come%20back%20to%20you.%20We%20are%20aware%20that%20there%20is%20a%20vacuum%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20filled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20has%20not%20made%20any%20suo%20motu%20statement%20on%20holding%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20after%202019.%20All%20the%20three%20statements%20made%20this%20year%20were%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20posed%20by%20journalists%20during%20news%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20seem%20nowhere%20in%20sight%2C%20even%20as%20the%20delimitation%20process%20was%20over%20on%20May%205%2C%202022%20and%20two%20revisions%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20have%20been%20undertaken%20by%20the%20poll%20body.%20The%20third%20revision%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20is%20currently%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20would%20be%20held%20after%20panchayat%20and%20municipal%20poll.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flet-alone-assembly-polls-even-local-body-elections-unlikely-in-jk-before-2024%5C%22%3Ealready%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20municipal%20and%20panchayat%20polls%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20held%20before%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EECI%E2%80%99s%20stance%20before%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%20was%20dissolved%20on%20November%2021%2C%202018%20by%20then%20Governor%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%20after%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20staked%20claim%20for%20formation%20of%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2010%2C%202019%2C%20the%20ECI%20announced%20that%20assembly%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20cannot%20be%20held%20along%20with%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20due%20to%20security%20concerns%2C%20even%20as%20major%20political%20parties%20had%20pushed%20for%20simultaneous%20polls%20during%20the%20poll%20body%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20the%20then%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Commission%20will%20be%20regularly%20and%20on%20real%20time%20basis%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20in%20J%20%26amp%3B%20K%20and%20will%20also%20be%20taking%20inputs%20from%20all%20necessary%20quarters%20and%20decision%20regarding%20holding%20Legislative%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20J%20%26amp%3B%20K%20will%20be%20taken%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ECI%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20then%20appointed%20three%20special%20observers%20to%20determine%20when%20assembly%20elections%20can%20be%20held%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20different%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20observers%20submitted%20their%20report%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20April%2015%2C%202019.%20In%20their%20report%2C%20they%20had%20reportedly%20suggested%20to%20the%20poll%20panel%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20conducive%20for%20elections%20immediately%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20June%204%2C%202019%2C%20the%20poll%20body%2C%20in%20a%20handout%2C%20said%20that%20holding%20polls%20should%20be%20considered%20later%20in%20the%20year.%20%E2%80%9CElection%20Commission%2C%20under%20Article%20324%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20other%20extant%20laws%2Frules%20etc.%20have%20unanimously%20decided%20that%20holding%20of%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20shall%20be%20considered%20later%20in%20this%20year.%20The%20Commission%20will%20keep%20on%20regularly%20and%20on%20real%20time%20basis%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20taking%20inputs%20from%20all%20necessary%20quarters%20and%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20will%20announce%20the%20election%20schedule%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20assembly%20election%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ECI%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUmer%20Maqbool%20is%20a%20Kashmir-based%20independent%20journalist%20writing%20on%20politics%2C%20governance%20and%20legal%20issues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697018444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F04125435%2Fsrinagar-23681285132975Y7qv.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-delimitation-over-2-voter-revisions-done-but-elections-nowhere-in-sight%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20from%20political%20and%20human%20rights%20actors%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Csuspension%20of%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-delimitation-over-2-voter-revisions-done-but-elections-nowhere-in-sight%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bola%20Tinubu%20diploma%3A%20No%20evidence%20Nigeria's%20president%20forged%20college%20record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697018409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17835%2Fproduction%2F_131390369_tinubu.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67067854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Allegations%20that%20Bola%20Tinubu's%20diplomas%20were%20fake%20went%20viral%20after%20the%20release%20of%20his%20school%20documents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67067854%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67067854.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67067854.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%2027-year-old%20Nick%20Simpson%20built%20the%20freelancing%20tax%20tool%20he%20wished%20he%20had%20and%20then%20raised%20%247.5%20million%20in%20venture%20funding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nick%20Simpson%20WorkMade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652585b855f52b01b35b3e5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENick%20Simpson%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20WorkMade.%3Cp%3EWorkMade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWorkMade%20is%20a%20new%20startup%20that%20lets%20freelancers%20keep%20track%20of%20their%20earnings%20and%20pay%20taxes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFrequent%20freelancer%20Nick%20Simpson%20founded%20WorkMade%20in%202022%20and%20scaled%20the%20startup%20to%2012%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20the%20startup%20is%20launching%20publicly%20with%20%247.5%20million%20in%20venture%20capital%20funding%20to%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Simpson%20has%20been%20freelancing%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2027-year-old%20founder%20of%20WorkMade%20landed%20his%20first%20for%20hire%20gig%20when%20he%20was%20just%209-years-old.%20He%20helped%20his%20neighbors%2C%20who%20were%20spa%20consultants%20at%20the%20time%2C%20build%20and%20design%20websites.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20nerd%20who%20would%20steal%20their%20Wi-Fi%20from%20the%20fence%20in%20the%20backyard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20made%20websites%20one%20day%20and%20I%20said%20yes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20turned%20those%20early%20gigs%20into%20a%20lucrative%20career%20as%20a%20designer%20for%20consumer-packaged-brands%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeverage-startup-hydrant-raises-8-million-from-aaron-rodgers-sloane-stephens-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydration%20supplement%20Hydrant%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20skincare%20scrub%20brand%20Becky%2C%20which%20he%20also%20founded..%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20throughout%20his%20working%20life%2C%20paying%20taxes%20on%20his%20freelance%20earnings%20has%20always%20been%20a%20huge%20hassle.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-freelancing-twice-before-making-six-figures-here-are-5-things-i-wish-id-known-earlier-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFreelancers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20to%20withhold%20taxes%20themselves%20when%20filing%20a%201099%20form%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20payment%20schedules%20can%20vary%20from%20state%20to%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20year%2C%20Simpson%20got%20a%20shocking%20notice%20that%20he%20owed%20%24140%2C000%20in%20taxes%2C%20but%20when%20he%20went%20to%20pay%20the%20bill%2C%20there%20was%20nowhere%20on%20the%20IRS%20website%20where%20he%20could%20do%20so%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20moment%20that%20I%20realized%20we%20were%20going%20to%20have%20a%20massive%20global%20tax%20issue%2C%20as%20the%20number%20of%20freelancers%20is%20only%20going%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20stressful%20incident%20was%20the%20catalyst%20for%20Simpson%20to%20found%20WorkMade%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20lets%20freelancers%20manage%2C%20withhold%2C%20and%20pay%20taxes%20on%20their%20business%20income%20all%20in%20one%20app.%20Founded%20in%202022%2C%20Simpson%20has%20grown%20the%20company%20to%2012%20employees%20and%20is%20launching%20the%20product%20to%20the%20public%20this%20month%2C%20after%20accruing%20a%20waitlist%20of%20over%2030%2C000%20sign%20ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20also%20raised%20%247.5%20million%20in%20venture%20capital%20funding%20to%20date%2C%20with%20top%20seed%20investors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-important-venture-capitalists-investors-in-los-angeles-2023-1%23anna-barber-m13-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAnna%20Barber's%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20M13%2C%201517%20Fund%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-best-women-early-stage-seed-vc-investors-startups-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGale%20Wilkinson's%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vitalize%20Venture%20Capital%2C%20and%20Slack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkMade%20offers%20business%20banking%20services%20for%20freelancers%2C%20supplied%20by%20Piermont%20Bank%20that%20includes%20a%20Mastercard%20debit%20card.%20When%20a%20customer%20signs%20up%20on%20the%20app%2C%20they're%20first%20prompted%20with%20a%20series%20of%20straightforward%20questions%20about%20how%20they%20typically%20file%20taxes%2C%20like%20whether%20they%20are%20single%20or%20married%2C%20filing%20jointly%20or%20separately%2C%20or%20use%20a%20vehicle%20for%20work%2C%20Simpson%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20users%20can%20then%20link%20bank%20accounts%20to%20indicate%20which%20expenses%20are%20personal%20and%20professional%2C%20and%20WorkMade%20automates%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20tax%20management%20process%20using%20AI%2C%20such%20as%20tracking%20tax%20write-offs%2C%20calculating%20taxes%20owed%20each%20quarter%20and%20putting%20aside%20the%20correct%20amount%20from%20their%20earnings%20for%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20time%20for%20a%20freelancer%20to%20pay%20their%20taxes%2C%20WorkMade%20manages%20that%20process%20too%2C%20including%20the%20payment%20without%20any%20forms%2C%20mail%20or%20extra%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20other%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.crunchbase.com%2Fjob-market%2Fcontract-workers-freelance-unicorn-startups-vc-jobandtalent-remote%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20startup%20tools%20for%20freelancers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20manage%20their%20gigs%20like%20Madrid's%20freelance%20work%20marketplace%20Jobsandtalent%20or%20Wellington%2C%20New%20Zealand's%20Hnry.%20But%20WorkMade%20differentiates%20itself%20by%20focusing%20solely%20on%20solving%20the%20problems%20around%20managing%20tax%20payments%20for%20US%20customers%2C%20Simpson%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20market%20for%20tools%20for%20freelancers%20in%20the%20US%20is%20a%20rapidly%20growing%20one.%20According%20to%20Statista%2C%20there%20are%20an%20estimated%2073%20million%20freelancers%20working%20in%20the%20US%20this%20year%2C%20and%20that%20number%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%20to%20over%2090%20million%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimpson%20plans%20to%20use%20this%20infusion%20of%20capital%20to%20continue%20to%20build%20new%20features%20for%20freelancers%20and%20acquire%20even%20more%20customers%20through%20future%20partnerships%20and%20word%20of%20mouth%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20somebody%20would%20have%20told%20me%20I'd%20be%20doing%20anything%20in%20taxes%2C%20banking%20and%20fintech%2C%20I%20would%20have%20laughed%20at%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Simpson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20feel%20like%20it's%20just%20added%20up%20to%20what%20I've%20been%20doing%20for%20nearly%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-workmade-solving-tax-challenges-us-freelancers-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697018402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652585b855f52b01b35b3e5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-workmade-solving-tax-challenges-us-freelancers-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20freelancer%20Nick%20Simpson%20was%20inspired%20by%20his%20experience%20dealing%20with%20taxes%20that%20led%20to%20launching%20WorkMade%20to%20help%20others%20with%20similar%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrenbarger%40insider.com%20(Madeline%20Renbarger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-workmade-solving-tax-challenges-us-freelancers-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Climate%20crisis%20will%20change%20taste%20of%20beer%20and%20make%20it%20more%20expensive%2C%20say%20scientists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697018280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768