y%20Guo%20and%20Dave%20Fontenot%20from%20Backend%20Capital.%20She%20was%20accepted%20into%20their%20September%2012-week%20cohort%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20her%20future%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20momentarily%20stepped%20away%20from%20high%20school.%20The%20accelerator%20became%20the%20launchpad%20and%20helped%20her%20in%20attracting%20investments%20from%20prominent%20names%20including%20On%20Deck%20and%20Village%20Global.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20explained%20that%20Delv.AI's%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20aid%20researchers%20in%20accessing%20specific%20information%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20online%20content.%20Delv.AI%20raised%20%24450%2C000%20(approximately%20Rs%203.7%20crore)%20in%20funding%20and%20currently%20boasts%20an%20approximate%20valuation%20of%20%2412%20million%20(Rs%20100%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697016480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ffp95brv_pranjali-awasthi_625x300_11_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2F16-year-old-indian-girls-ai-company-launched-in-2022-now-valued-at-rs-100-crore-4470684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pranjali%20Awasthi's%20Delv.AI%20raised%20Rs%203.7%20crore%20in%20funding%20and%20currently%20boasts%20an%20approximate%20valuation%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2F16-year-old-indian-girls-ai-company-launched-in-2022-now-valued-at-rs-100-crore-4470684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2F16-year-old-indian-girls-ai-company-launched-in-2022-now-valued-at-rs-100-crore-4470684%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2F16-year-old-indian-girls-ai-company-launched-in-2022-now-valued-at-rs-100-crore-4470684%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here%20are%20the%20CEOs%20and%20investors%20who%20want%20Ha