n%20being%20set%20on%20fire%20in%20a%20harrowing%20video%20that%20was%20widely%20circulated%20October%208%2C%20top%20sources%20have%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20family%20of%20the%20man%20police%20has%20claimed%20he%20is%20have%20also%20said%20the%20man%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20is%20not%20their%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20this%20on%20October%2010%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Manipur%20security%20advisor%2C%20retired%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%20Kuldiep%20Singh%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fvideo%2Fmanipur-security-advisor-recommends-cbi-to-probe-into-the-viral-video-of-tribal-mans-body-allegedly-burnt-691749-2023-10-09%3Futm_source%3Ditneweb_video_share%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20police%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20the%20video%20and%20has%20been%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20a%20man%20is%20seen%20being%20burnt%2C%20with%20at%20least%20three%20men%20present%20nearby.%20His%20face%20is%20visible.%20Bullets%20are%20also%20seen%20and%20heard%20being%20fired%20in%20the%20video.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20from%20May%204th%2C%20and%20the%20person%E2%80%99s%20body%20is%20lying%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20JNIMS%20hospital%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20person%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20Laldinthanga%20Khongsai%2C%2037%2C%20%5Bhe%20is%20the%5D%20son%20of%20Zamtinmang%20Khongsai%2C%20and%20he%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Khomching%20village%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20also%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20case%20has%20already%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20by%20the%20DGP%2C%20Rajiv%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMembers%20of%20The%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%2C%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20also%20shared%20the%20video%20with%20reporters