%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20how%20bodies%20are%20lying%20unclaimed%20in%20hospitals.%20While%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20had%20claimed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20most%20of%20the%20bodies%20still%20in%20morgues%20of%20Imphal%20are%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsg-tushar-mehtas-claim-that-unclaimed-bodies-in-manipur-belong-to-infiltrators-is-unfounded%5C%22%3Ethis%20was%20found%20to%20be%20unfounded%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EComparatively%20fewer%20bodies%20are%20unidentified%20than%20are%20unclaimed%20as%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20are%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20Imphal%20due%20to%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kuki%20Student%20Organisation%20(KSO)%20had%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20were%20ready%20to%20verify%20all%20the%20bodies%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20morgues%2C%20with%20all%20the%20relevant%20documents%2C%20if%20provided%20with%20the%20necessary%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20calls%20to%20Kuldiep%20Singh%20have%20not%20been%20answered.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20they%20are.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697015389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-kuldiep-singh-burnt-man-video%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20police%20sources%20and%20the%20family%20of%20Laldinthanga%20Khongsai%20have%20said%20there%20are%20grave%20doubts%20on%20whether%20he%20is%20the%20victim%20seen%20in%20a%20harrowing%20burning%20video.%20Police%20had%2C%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20identified%20the%20victim%20in%20the%20video%20as%20such.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-kuldiep-singh-burnt-man-video%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2