f%20India%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20case%20was%20linked%20to%20causing%20disruption%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Bihar%20last%20year.%20The%20NIA%20took%20over%20the%20case%2C%20originally%20registered%20by%20Phulwari%20Sharif%20police%20station%20in%20Patna%20in%20July%202022%2C%20against%20Popular%20Front%20of%20India%20(PFI)%20members%20for%20conspiring%20to%20disrupt%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20visit%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20officer%20told%20the%20media.%20Similar%20raids%20are%20carried%20out%20at%20multiple%20locations%2C%20the%20police%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20six%20hours%20that%20the%20police%20had%20gheroed%20Shaikh%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20he%20had%20already%20written%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20and%20contacted%20media%20persons.%20He%20had%20also%20put%20out%20a%20recorded%20video%20statement%20describing%20the%20ordeal%20he%20and%20his%20family%20were%20put%20through.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20broken%20one%20of%20the%20two%20doors%20to%20my%20house.%20They%20have%20also%20broken%20the%20CCTV%20mounted%20outside%20my%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5S3qVTFSoCo%3Fsi%3DKZRvztJPI9O1UUO3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EShaikh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20lower-middle-class%20Mumbai%20suburb%20of%20Vikhroli%2C%20teaches%20at%20Anjuman-i-Islam%20Abdus%20Sattar%20Shoaib%20School.%20After%20a%20prolonged%20incarceration%20of%20nine%20years%2C%20when%20Shaikh%20was%20finally%20released%20in%202015%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20study%20law.%20He%20is%20presently%20pursuing%20a%20PhD%20and%20also%20runs%20%E2%80%98Innocence%20Network%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20loosely%20run%20collective%