e%20was%20the%20first%20woman%20minister%20of%20Puducherry%20in%2040%20years%20and%20took%20oath%20in%20July%202021%20as%20the%20lone%20woman%20member%20of%20the%20cabinet%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fpuducherry%2Fpuducherrys-lone-woman-minister-resigns-citing-caste-and-gender-discrimination-in-ainrc-bjp-govt-2720779%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5lejQf9uHy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5lejQf9uHy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Chandirapriyanga%20(%40SPriyanga_offl)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSPriyanga_offl%2Fstatus%2F1711646415909454054%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20entered%20the%20Assembly%20through%20people%E2%80%99s%20confidence%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20it%20is%20not%20so%20easy%20to%20overcome%20the%20politics%20of%20conspiracy.%20I%20could%20not%20continue%20my%20fight%20against%20money%20power.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20pride%20over%20my%20Dalit%20identity%20was%20the%20problem%20for%20others.%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20being%20continuously%20subjected%20to%20caste%20and%20gender%20bias%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20he%20would%20respond%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmindless%20criticism%E2%80%9D%20received%20by%20her%20by%20releasing%20a%20list%20of%20her%20achievements%20as%20a%20minister%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20indebted%20to%20the%20people%20who%20elected%20me%20as%20a%20legislator.%20But%20I%20resign%20my%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20as%20I%20realise%20that%20I%20cannot%20continuously%20fight%20against%20dominant%20forces.%20I%20apologise%20to%20my%20voters%20for%20resigning%20as%20a%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20thanking%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20become%20a%20minister%2C%20Priyanga%20requested%20him%20to%20accept%20her%20resignation%20and%20appoint%20a%20person%20from%20a%20minority%20community%20in%20her%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20them%20trying%20to%20get%20Cabinet%20power%20through%20money%20power%20should%20be%20accommodated%20as%20it%20will%20cause%20injustice%20to%20the%20dominant%20Dalit%20and%20Vanniyar%20communities.%20So%20one%20of%20the%20legislators%20belonging%20to%20Dalit%2C%20Vanniyar%20or%20minority%20community%20should%20be%20given%20the%20cabinet%20berth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priyanga%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20requested%20him%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20no%20interruptions%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20her%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697011244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11122610%2FF7SLM94XsAA25sF.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fpuducherry-lone-woman-minister-chandira-priyanga-resigns-over-alleged-caste-gender-discrimination%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20was%20the%20only%20woman%20legislator%20in%20the%2030-member%20assembly%20and%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20lead%20a%20ministry%20since%201983.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fpuducherry-lone-woman-minister-chandira-priyanga-resigns-over-alleged-caste-gender-discrimination%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yagira%20Yuya%2C%20Asian%20Content%20Award%20Winner%2C%20Talks%20%E2%80%98Gannibal%E2%80%99%20Second%20Season%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697011238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGannibal-cr.jpg%3Fw%3D1000