ng%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20employees%20and%20their%20families.%20Below%20is%20a%20message%20we%20shared%20with%20Microsoft%20employees%20today%20about%20our%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHeartbroken%20by%20the%20horrific%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20and%20the%20escalating%20conflict.%20My%20deepest%20condolences%20are%20with%20all%20those%20killed%20and%20impacted.%20Our%20focus%20remains%20on%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20employees%20and%20their%20families.%20Below%20is%20a%20message%20we%20shared%20with%20Microsoft%20employees%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Satya%20Nadella%20(%40satyanadella)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsatyanadella%2Fstatus%2F1711979964709605518%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shared%20the%20message%20that%20went%20out%20to%20employees%20in%20Israel%20by%20Kathleen%20Hogan%2C%20Executive%20Vice%20President%20and%20Chief%20Human%20Resources%20Officer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20profoundly%20saddened%20by%20the%20horrific%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20this%20weekend%20and%20the%20atrocities%20we%20continue%20to%20watch%20unfold.%20Together%20with%20the%20senior%20leadership%20team%20(SLT)%2C%20I%20want%20to%20express%20my%20deepest%20sympathy%20for%20those%20who%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20injured%2C%20lost%20loved%20ones%2C%20and%20all%20those%20impacted%20by%20this%20violence.%20Together%20we%20condemn%20this%20hatred%20and%20brutality%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Hogan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outpouring%20of%20support%20from%20so%20many%20of%20you%20worldwide%20is%20heartfelt%20and%20needed%20now%2C%20and%20many%20of%20you%20are%20asking%20how%20you%20can%20help.%20Since%20the%20attacks%20unfolded%20on%20Saturday%2C%20we%20have%20been%20f