20week%20or%20even%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Saxena%2C%20a%20high%20official%20of%20the%20government%2C%20went%20back%2013%20years%20to%20draw%20from%20a%20complaint%20filed%20on%20October%2028%2C%202010%2C%20by%20Sushil%20Pandit%20against%20Roy%2C%20Hussein%20and%20two%20men%20who%20have%20since%20died%20(Syed%20Ali%20Shah%20Geelani%20and%20Syed%20Abdul%20Rahman%20Geelani).%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-puts-sedition-law-in-abeyance-during-government-review%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cases%20of%20sedition%20could%20not%20advance%20while%20the%20government%20reviews%20the%20law.%20Saxena%20noted%20that%20while%20a%20%E2%80%98case%20of%20sedition%20is%20made%20out%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20police%20itself%20was%20not%20pressing%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20staying%20all%20sedition%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20by%20the%20government%20against%20Roy%20and%20Hussein%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3Eraids%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20homes%20and%20offices%20of%20journalists%20and%20researchers%20across%20India.%20On%20October%203%2C%20500%20officials%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20interrogated%20reporters%20associated%20with%20the%20news%20website%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterpunch.org%2F2023%2F10%2F04%2Fmy-friends-prabir-and-amit-are-in-jail-in-india-for-their-work-in-the-media%2F%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20founder%20(Prabir%20Purkayastha)%20and%20its%20human%20resources%20head%20(Amit%20Chakraborty)%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%3B%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20have%20now%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnewsclick-case-purkayasthan-chakravarti-10-days-judicial-custody%5C%22%3Emoved%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20police%20to%20judicial%20custody%20and%20are%20in%20jail.%20The%20raids%20and%20arrests%20provoked%20mass%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fnewsclick-arrests-journalists-and-activists-hold-protest-against-attack-on-press-freedom%2Farticle67393199.ece%5C%22%3Edemonstrations%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country%20in%20defence%20of%20press%20freedom.%20The%20day%20after%20the%20raid%20and%20arrests%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmore-dangerous-emergency-arundhati-roy-raids-journalists-newsclick%5C%22%3Eprotest%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20held%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Roy%20sat%20prominently%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20room%20with%20a%20sign%20around%20her%20neck%20that%20read%2C%20%E2%80%98Free%20the%20Press%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Throttling%20What%20Remains%20of%20Independent%20Media%20in%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthrottling-what-remains-of-independent-media-in-india%5C%22%3EThrottling%20What%20Remains%20of%20Independent%20Media%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20no%20surprise%20that%20Roy%20was%20at%20the%20protest.%20Since%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebookerprizes.com%2Fthe-booker-library%2Fbooks%2Fthe-god-of-small-things%5C%22%3Ewon%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Booker%20Prize%20for%20her%20landmark%20novel%20%3Cem%3EA%20God%20of%20Small%20Things%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201997%2C%20Roy%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20imperialism%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20toxic%20right-wing%20Hindutva%20movement.%20After%20India%E2%80%99s%20nuclear%20test%20in%201998%2C%20she%20wrote%20a%20brave%20essay%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fstory%2Fthe-end-of-imagination%2F205932%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%2