%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202019).%20In%20her%20fabulous%20IG%20Khan%20Memorial%20Lecture%20in%20April%202004%2C%20Roy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fwebsite%2Fstory%2Fhow-deep-shall-we-dig%2F223821%5C%22%3Echaracterised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20developments%20in%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98dual%20orchestra%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98While%20one%20arm%20is%20busy%20selling%20off%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20assets%20in%20chunks%2C%20the%20other%2C%20to%20divert%20attention%2C%20is%20arranging%20a%20baying%2C%20howling%20deranged%20chorus%20of%20cultural%20nationalism%E2%80%99.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20was%20in%20power%20at%20that%20time%20but%20would%20lose%20the%20elections%20the%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20an%20elephantine%20memory.%20Nothing%20of%20these%20kinds%20of%20remarks%20is%20forgotten.%20Everything%20is%20remembered.%20The%20BJP%20returns%20at%20some%20point%20to%20cash%20its%20cheque.%20Roy%20made%20a%20speech%20in%202010.%20It%20was%20not%20forgotten.%20She%20was%20at%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20arrest%20of%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty.%20The%20FIR%20against%20her%20has%20been%20activated%20by%20the%20LG%20less%20than%20a%20week%20later.%20The%20FIR%20is%20not%20just%20about%20that%20speech%20in%202010.%20It%20is%20against%20everything%20she%20has%20stood%20for%20since%20%E2%80%98The%20End%20of%20Imagination%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKashmir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20in%202010%3F%20So%20much%20happens%20in%20Kashmir%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20remember%20the%20details%20of%20even%20last%20year%2C%20let%20alone%20so%20many%20years%20ago.%20In%20April%202010%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20shot%20dead%20three%20civilians%20from%20Rafiabad%20and%20then%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20infiltrated%20from%20Pakistan.%20The%20murders%20took%20place%20so%20that%20the%20soldiers%20could%20claim%20cash%20rewards%20being%20offered%20for%20such%20killings%3B%20five%20soldiers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2FMachil-fake-encounter-Seven-soldiers-sentenced-to-life-for-killing-three-Kashmiri-civilians%2Farticle61760367.ece%5C%22%3Ereceived%3C%2Fa%3E%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20their%20actions%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmachil-fake-encounter-armed-forces-tribunal-suspends-life-imprisonment-of-five-armymen%2F%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Tribunal%20in%202017).%20Inevitably%2C%20large%20mobilisations%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20other%20places%20demanded%20the%20complete%20de-militarisation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(it%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20military-to-civilian%20ratios%20%E2%80%93%20one%20million%20soldiers%20to%2014%20million%20residents).%20The%20protests%20led%20to%20more%20military%20violence%2C%20which%20then%20led%20to%20more%20anger%20and%20mobilisations.%20By%20September%2C%20these%20protests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2FCurfew-in-all-major-towns-of-Kashmir%2Farticle15974870.ece%5C%22%3Ebecame%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20mass%20movement%2C%20and%20so%20the%20Indian%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2FManmohan-announces-over-Rs.1000-crore-sops-for-JampK%2Farticle16242028.ece%5C%22%3Eoffered%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20concessions%20to%20calm%20matters.%20The%20public%20meeting%20held%20in%20Delhi%20on%20October%2021%20was%20part%20of%20this%20cycle%20of%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Roy%20had%20travelled%20to%20Kashmir.%20Since%201987%2C%20it%20has%20been%20relatively%20impossible%20to%20be%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20not%20experience%20either%20terrible%20violence%20or%20a%20mass%20demonstration.%20She%20was%20fortunate%20to%20be%20there%20at%20a%20time%20when%20a%20major%20non-violent%20uprising%20resulted%20in%20the%20ordinary%20people%20of%20Srinagar%20taking%20over%20their%20city.%20In%20an%20essay%20in%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Roy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fstory%2Fazadi%2F238272%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20city%20floated%20on%20a%20sea%20of%20smiles.%20There%20was%20ecstasy%20in%20the%20air.%20Everyone%20had%20a%20banner%3A%20houseboat%20owners%2C%20traders%2C%20students%2C%20lawyers%2C%20doctors.%20One%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20prisoners%2C%20set%20us%20free%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoy%20went%20to%20a%20rally%20addressed%20by%20Syed%20Ali%20Shah%20Geelani%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Tehreek-e-Hurriyat.%20She%20writes%20about%20how%20uncomfortable%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20the%20movement%20made%20her%20(%E2%80%98I%20imagined%20myself%20standing%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20Hindu%20nationalist%20rally%E2%80%A6Replace%20the%20word%20Islam%20with%20the%20word%20Hindutva%2C%20replace%20the%20word%20Pakistan%20with%20Hindustan%2C%20replace%20the%20green%20flags%20with%20saffron%20ones%2C%20and%20we%20would%20have%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20nightmare%20vision%20of%20an%20ideal%20India%E2%80%99).%20Roy%20stood%20there%20to%20observe%20the%20spontaneous%20energy%20of%20a%20people%20seeking%20to%20exit%20the%20militarisation%20of%20their%20society%2C%20but%20she%20was%20not%20standing%20there%20to%20cheer%20on%20the%20immediate%20options%20that%20lay%20available%20to%20them.%20To%20characterise%20her%20one-dimensionally%20is%20to%20miss%20the%20writer%20in%20Roy%2C%20who%20seeks%20nuance%20and%20moral%20ambiguity%20%E2%80%93%20two%20qualities%20lost%20to%20the%20rigidities%20of%20the%20hard%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'More%20Dangerous%20Than%20Emergency'%3A%20Arundhati%20Roy%20on%20Raiding%20of%20Journalists%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmore-dangerous-emergency-arundhati-roy-raids-journalists-newsclick%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98More%20Dangerous%20Than%20Emergency%E2%80%99%3A%20Arundhati%20Roy%20on%20Raiding%20of%20Journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20with%20that%20strong%20sense%20of%20the%20democratic%20potential%20in%20the%20world%20that%20Roy%20joined%20Geelani%20at%20the%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20October%2021%2C%202010.%20The%20conference%20she%20attended%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Committee%20for%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners.%20The%20banner%20behind%20the%20podium%20read%2C%20%E2%80%98Azadi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Only%20Way%E2%80%99.%20The%20word%20%3Cem%3Eazadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20come%20in%20for%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20confusion%20since%20that%20time%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20struggle%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20when%20the%20students%20in%202016%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2FJNUSU-leader-Kanhaiya-Kumar-speech-after-release%2Farticle60529871.ece%5C%22%3Echanted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20word%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20their%20frustration%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20and%20what%20was%20happening%20to%20education.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%93%20which%20means%20freedom%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20used%20by%20Indian%20nationalists%20against%20British%20rule%20as%20well%20as%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Flifestyle%2Flife-style%2Fkamla-bhasin-azadi-slogan-origin-meaning-7533612%2F%5C%22%3Efeminists%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20patriarchy.%20It%20is%20not%20especially%20associated%20with%20Kashmir%2C%20although%20sections%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20movement%20use%20it%20as%20part%20of%20their%20secessionist%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESushil%20Pandit%2C%20a%20right-wing%20activist%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20family%2C%20decided%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Tilak%20Marg%20police%20station%20against%20Roy%20(this%2C%20despite%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20careful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fstory%2Fazadi%2F238272%5C%22%3Eattention%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20plight%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20who%20left%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20the%201990s).%20A%20FIR%20was%20registered%2C%20charging%20Roy%20with%20sedition%20(Section%20124A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code)%2C%20UAPA%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20other%20sections%20of%20law.%20She%20did%20not%20back%20down.%20She%20held%20her%20own.%20Nothing%20came%20of%20Pandit%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20%E2%80%93%20at%20that%20time%20or%20for%20another%2013%20years%20%E2%80%93%20because%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201990s%2C%20Roy%20began%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20negative%20impacts%20of%20capitalist%20development.%20She%20spent%20time%20with%20the%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20a%20movement%20led%20by%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20that%20wanted%20to%20prevent%20the%20displacement%20of%20large%20numbers%20of%20small%20farmers%20from%20their%20land%20to%20build%20a%20large%20dam%20complex.%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20essay%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98The%20Greater%20Common%20Good%E2%80%99%20(1999)%20%E2%80%93%20took%20issue%20with%20the%20Big%20Projects.%20As%20if%20echoing%20the%20title%20of%20her%20novel%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20God%20of%20Small%20Things%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Roy%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%98Perhaps%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20the%20Twenty%E2%80%93first%20century%20has%20in%20store%20for%20us.%20The%20dismantling%20of%20the%20Big.%20Big%20bombs%2C%20big%20dams%2C%20big%20ideologies%2C%20big%20contradictions%2C%20big%20countries%2C%20big%20wars%2C%20big%20heroes%2C%20big%20mistakes.%20Perhaps%20it%20will%20be%20the%20Century%20of%20the%20Small.%20Perhaps%20right%20now%2C%20this%20very%20minute%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20god%20up%20in%20heaven%20readying%20herself%20for%20us.%20Could%20it%20be%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20essay%20is%20often%20misunderstood.%20Roy%20does%20not%20want%20to%20condemn%20the%20people%20of%20India%20to%20a%20life%20without%20electricity.%20She%20is%20attentive%20to%20the%20importance%20of%20modernity%2C%20but%20asks%20the%20simple%20question%3A%20modernity%20for%20whom%3F%20The%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20who%20will%20be%20displaced%20from%20the%20villages%20of%20the%20Narmada%20will%20not%20be%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20project%3B%20the%20beneficiary%20will%20be%20large%20capital%2C%20which%20will%20use%20the%20electricity%20%E2%80%93%20at%20a%20government%20subsidised%20price%20%E2%80%93%20to%20strengthen%20its%20control%20over%20the%20Indian%20economy.%20The%20poor%20will%20vanish.%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20puncture%20the%20myth%20about%20the%20inefficient%2C%20humbling%2C%20corrupt%2C%20but%20ultimately%20genial%2C%20essentially%20democratic%2C%20Indian%20State%2C%E2%80%99%20Roy%20writes.%20%E2%80%98Carelessness%20cannot%20account%20for%20fifty%20million%20disappeared%20people.%20Nor%20can%20Karma.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20not%20delude%20our%C2%ADselves.%20There%20is%20method%20here%2C%20precise%2C%20relentless%2C%20and%20one%20hundred%20percent%20man-made%E2%80%99.%20That%20method%20is%20the%20efficient%20use%20of%20the%20State%20by%20capital%20for%20its%20own%20interest.%20This%20efficiency%20was%20going%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F8d46b435-9725-46d4-80be-2cb3e276c4c9%5C%22%3Emobilised%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20good%20effect%20by%20Gautam%20Adani%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20%E2%80%93%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%20in%202014%20%E2%80%93%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Patkar%20and%20Roy%20wanted%20to%20lift%20up%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20V.K.%20Saxena%2C%20a%20businessman%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20set%20up%20the%20National%20Council%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20in%20India%20in%201991%20to%20champion%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20corporate%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaxena%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eb%C3%AAte%20noire%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20Patkar%2C%20who%20had%20begun%20to%20gain%20popularity%20within%20sections%20of%20India%20and%20had%20been%20able%20to%20force%20the%20World%20Bank%20to%20review%20the%20Narmada%20project%20with%20her%20protests.%20On%20April%2010%2C%202002%2C%20Saxena%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2F2002-assault-on-medha-patkar-at-sabarmati-ashram-delhi-l-g-seeks-immunity-from-trial-1197986.html%5C%22%3Ewent%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20politicians%20from%20the%20BJP%20(Amit%20P.%20Shah%20and%20Amit%20D.%20Thaker)%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%20(Rohit%20N.%20Patel)%20to%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Sabarmati%20Ashram.%20Patkar%20was%20at%20a%20meeting%20being%20held%20there%20to%20galvanise%20a%20peace%20movement%20during%20the%20anti-Muslim%20violence%20of%202002.%20Saxena%20and%20the%20other%20politicians%20are%20accused%20of%20physically%20assaulting%20Patkar%20at%20this%20meeting.%20A%20First%20Information%20Report%20was%20filed%20against%20Saxena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20as%20his%20political%20power%20grew%20through%20proximity%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20Saxena%20has%20been%20able%20to%20hold%20off%20the%20impact%20of%20that%20FIR.%20In%20May%202022%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20appointed%20Saxena%20lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Delhi.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Sanjay%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Faap-sanjay-singh-attacks-delhi-l-g-vk-saxena-over-2002-sabarmati-ashram-assault-case-2343879-2023-03-07%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20issue%20of%20the%202002%20assault%20to%20no%20avail.%20(Singh%2C%20incidentally%2C%20has%20himself%20now%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-conducts-searches-at-aap-mp-sanjay-singhs-house%5C%22%3Earrested%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Farrest-of-sanjay-singh-completely-illegal-reflects-pm-modis-nervousness-arvind-kejriwal%2Farticleshow%2F104165018.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eillegally%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20his%20party%20%E2%80%93%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20liquor%20scam%20just%20days%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty.)%20Undeterred%20by%20Singh%2C%20Saxena%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Fdelhi-lg-v-k-saxena-seeks-immunity-wants-trial-put-in-abeyance%2Farticleshow%2F98463578.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Emoved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20courts%20against%20the%20FIR%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20has%20immunity%20as%20a%20nominee%20of%20the%20President%20of%20India.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20this%20May%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2F2002-assault-vinai-saxena-gujarat-hc-8823837%2F%5C%22%3Egave%3C%2Fa%3E%20Saxena%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20the%20case.%20Now%2C%20Saxena%20has%20lifted%20out%20of%20his%20drawer%20the%20old%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Pandit%20to%20go%20after%20Patkar%E2%80%99s%20close%20friend%20and%20comrade%2C%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2012%2C%202023%2C%20Roy%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%202023%20European%20Essay%20Award.%20The%20honour%20went%20to%20essays%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98The%20Greater%20Common%20Good%E2%80%99.%20In%20her%20acceptance%20speech%2C%20Roy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055943%2Farundhati-roy-the-dismantling-of-democracy-in-india-will-affect-the-whole-world%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20today%20%E2%80%98it%20is%20unthinkable%20that%20any%20mainstream%20media%20house%20in%20India%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20live%20on%20corporate%20advertisements%2C%20would%20publish%20essays%20like%20these.%20In%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20the%20free%20market%20and%20fascism%20and%20the%20so-called%20free%20press%2C%20have%20waltzed%20together%20to%20bring%20India%20to%20a%20place%20where%20it%20can%20by%20no%20means%20be%20called%20a%20democracy.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20and%20the%20threats%20against%20Roy%20and%20Hussain%20are%20part%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98dismantling%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99.%20That%20%E2%80%98small%20god%20up%20in%20heaven%E2%80%99%20that%20Roy%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20listen%20to%20in%201999%20must%20shudder%20every%20time%20she%20turns%20her%20eyes%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVijay%20Prashad%20is%20the%20director%20of%20Tricontinental%3A%20Institute%20for%20Social%20Research.%20His%20latest%20book%20%E2%80%93%20written%20with%20Noam%20Chomsky%20%E2%80%93%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Withdrawal%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697010268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11122534%2FScreenshot-2023-10-11-at-12.22.52-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-is-the-indian-state-reigniting-a-13-year-old-case-against-arundhati-roy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FIR%20is%20not%20just%20about%20a%20speech%20in%202010.%20It%20is%20against%20everything%20she%20has%20stood%20for%20since%20her%201998%20essay%20%E2%80%98The%20End%20of%20Imagination%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-is-the-indian-state-reigniting-a-13-year-old-case-against-arundhati-roy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%3A%20Anger%20Among%20Sections%20of%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20Mostly%20Raje%20Loyalists%20%E2%80%93%20After%20Ticket%20Snubs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11130600%2FF77MUslboAAREWC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20candidates%20list%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20led%20to%20anger%2C%20shock%20and%20degrees%20of%20dissatisfaction%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2041%20candidates%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20is%20attempting%20to%20wrest%20power%20from%20the%20incumbent%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frajasthan-bjp-changes-five-time-mla-snubbed-8976537%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20it%20that%20Narpat%20Singh%20Rajvi%2C%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20the%20former%20vice-president%20of%20India%2C%20is%20angered%20at%20the%20snub%20he%20has%20received.%20Rajvi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar%2C%20was%20overlooked%20for%20the%20constituency%20he%20holds%20for%20Jaipur%20royal%20Diya%20Kumari.%20Rajvi%20is%20a%20five-time%20MLA%2C%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%2C%20and%20believed%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Vasundhara%20Raje.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20observes%20the%20snub%20as%20something%20reflective%20of%20a%20generational%20change%20in%20BJP%2C%20where%20the%20relative%20of%20one%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20original%20founders%20would%20earlier%20have%20been%20a%20shoe-in%20for%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-elections%2Frajasthan%2Fnews%2Fdenied-tickets-raje-loyalists-in-shock%2Farticleshow%2F104325398.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20Raje%20loyalist%20has%20been%20unhappy%20and%20even%20met%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20after%20having%20been%20dropped%20as%20the%20Jhotwara%20candidate.%20Rajpal%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20is%20a%20former%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%2C%20a%20two-time%20MLA%2C%20Anita%20Gurjar%2C%20has%20announced%20that%20she%20will%20contest%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate.%20Gurjar%20has%20openly%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20treated%20thus%20as%20she%20is%20close%20to%20Raje.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%20feeling%20%E2%80%9Cleft%20o