0%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20were%20revealed%20when%20Vinod%20Rai%20was%20the%20CAG%2C%20and%20which%20had%20serious%20consequences%20for%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20credibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20learnt%20that%20two%20of%20the%20Indian%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20Service%20(IA%26amp%3BAS)%20officers%20who%20were%20transferred%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20audit%20reports%20that%20exposed%20corruption%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20and%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20third%20officer%20who%20had%20initiated%20the%20audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20report%20was%20also%20transferred.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20order%201901%20of%20the%20CAG%20office%20dated%20September%2012%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EAtoorva%20Sinha%20who%20was%20the%20principal%20director%20of%20audit%2C%20Infrastructure%20(PDA%2C%20Infrastructure)%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20transferred%20and%20posted%20as%20Accountant%20General%20(A%26amp%3BE)%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Thiruvananthapuram%20in%20place%20of%20Sunil%20Raj%20Somarajan.%20Sinha%20was%20only%20assigned%20the%20PDA%2C%20Infrastructure%20post%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20order%20adds%20that%20the%20additional%20charge%20of%20the%20post%20of%20PDA%2C%20Infrastructure%20will%20be%20held%20by%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20Pandey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAtoova%20Sinha%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20CAG%20report%20on%20highway%20projects%20under%20the%20Implementation%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20Phase-I%20(BPP-1)%20that%20found%20instances%20of%20irregularities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20found%20massive%20overrun%20costs%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20and%20said%20that%20the%20National%20Highway%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20opt%20for%20an%20elevated%20carriageway%20in%20the%20Haryana%20portion%20pushed%20up%20costs%20to%20Rs%20250.77%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20as%20against%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%2018.20%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20approved%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FDwarkaExpressway_Linkedin.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FDwarkaExpressway_Linkedin.jpg%20698w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FDwarkaExpressway_Linkedin-300x172.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-52086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDwarka%20Expressway.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EPhoto%3A%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20order%201902%20of%20the%20CAG%20office%2C%20also%20dated%20September%2012%2C%20Dattaprasad%20Suryakant%20Shirsat%20Director%20(AMG%20II)%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Audit%2C%20Central%20Expenditure%2C%20New%20Delhi%20%E2%80%9Chas%20been%20transferred%20and%20posted%20as%20Director%20(legal)%20in%20this%20office%20against%20an%20existing%20vacancy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20learnt%20that%20Shirsat%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Performance%20Audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20Government%20(Civil)%20National%20Health%20Authority%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20that%20exposed%20corruption%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20healthcare%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20order%20also%20states%20that%20Ashok%20Sinha%2C%20director%20general%20(North%20Central%20Region)%20has%20been%20transferred%20as%20director%20general%20Rajbhasha.%20He%20will%20also%20hold%20the%20additional%20charge%20of%20the%20post%20of%20director%20general%20(exam)%20in%20the%20CAG%20office%20%E2%80%9Ctill%20further%20orders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20learnt%20that%20Sinha%20had%20initiated%20the%20audit%20of%20Performance%20Audit%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20Government%20(Civil)%20National%20Health%20Authority%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20audit%20report%20revealed%20corruption%20in%20insurance%20settlement%20claims.%20The%20report%2C%20among%20other%20findings%2C%20said%20that%20lakhs%20of%20claims%20continued%20to%20be%20made%20against%20some%20who%20had%20been%20shown%20as%20%E2%80%98deceased%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20database.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20CAG%20office%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20transfers.%20These%20transfer%20and%20posting%20orders%20involving%20a%20total%20of%2037%20officers%20have%20not%20been%20posted%20online.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20reports%20on%20the%20irregularities%20in%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%20were%20in%20particular%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20%E2%80%93%20who%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20of%20presiding%20over%20%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D%2C%20demanding%20accountability%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20CAG%20is%20Girish%20Chandra%20Murmu%2C%20who%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-resigning-as-jk-lg-g-c-murmu-appointed-as-new-cag%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eappointed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202020.%20Murmu%20is%20a%201985-batch%20Gujarat%20cadre%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20both%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Prior%20to%20his%20appointment%20as%20the%20CAG%2C%20Murmu%20was%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-shahs-trusted-aide-girish-chandra-murmu-appointed-lg-of-jk%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20downgrading%20its%20status%20to%20a%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20the%20CAG%20report%20on%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20said%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-nhai-toll-collection-railway-bharatmala-udan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eon%20highway%20projects%20under%20the%20Implementation%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20Phase-I%20(BPP-1)%20found%20huge%20overrun%20costs%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project%2C%20which%20was%20prioritised%20to%20decongest%20NH-48%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Gurugram%20by%20developing%20it%20into%20a%2014-lane%20national%20highway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20the%20NHAI%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20opt%20for%20an%20elevated%20carriageway%20in%20the%20Haryana%20portion%20pushed%20up%20costs%20to%20Rs%20250.77%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20from%20the%20approved%20cost%20of%20Rs%2018.20%20crore%20per%20kilometre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20the%20NHAI%20board%20approved%20the%20Delhi-Vadodara%20Expressway%20with%20a%20civil%20cost%20of%20around%20Rs%2032%2C839%20crore%2C%20which%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20CCEA-approved%20list%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20Phase-I%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%20irregularities%20in%20the%20award%20of%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInstances%20of%20irregularities%20in%20award%20of%20projects%20by%20implementing%20agencies%20were%20observed%20in%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20prescribed%20processes%20of%20tendering%2C%20viz.%2C%20successful%20bidder%20not%20fulfilling%20tender%20condition%20or%20bidder%20selected%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20falsified%20documents%2C%20award%20of%20works%20without%20there%20being%20approved%20detailed%20project%20reports%20or%20based%20on%20faulty%20detailed%20project%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20report%20was%20released%2C%20the%20AAP%20held%20a%20protest%20at%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20and%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Faap-protests-at-dwarka-expressway-over-irregularities-flagged-by-cag-report-8894745%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cbreaking%20all%20records%20of%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20was%20also%20used%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20flag%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSupriyaShrinate%2Fstatus%2F1691811461473939920%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20the%20CAG%20report%20on%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20said%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20Performance%20Audit%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20Government%20(Civil)%20National%20Health%20Authority%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20%E2%80%93%20found%20several%20instances%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20report%2C%20964%20hospitals%20in%20161%20districts%20of%20all%2028%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20(UTs)%20were%20audited.%20Delhi%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20have%20opted%20out%20of%20this%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20audit%20revealed%20corruption%20in%20insurance%20settlement%20claims%20and%20found%20that%20in%202.25%20lakh%20cases%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98surgery%E2%80%99%20done%20was%20shown%20to%20be%20later%20than%20the%20date%20of%20discharge.%20More%20than%201.79%20lakh%20such%20cases%20were%20found%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20for%20which%20the%20claimed%20amount%20was%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELakhs%20of%20claims%20continued%20to%20be%20made%20against%20some%20who%20had%20been%20shown%20as%20%E2%80%98deceased%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20database.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20audit%20also%20discovered%20that%201.57%20lakh%20unique%20IDs%20appeared%20more%20than%20once%20in%20the%20database%20even%20though%20the%20scheme%20stipulates%20that%20a%20unique%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PMJAY)%20ID%20should%20be%20issued%20to%20beneficiaries%20once%20verification%20is%20complete.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20CAG%20report%20was%20reported%20widely%2C%20including%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20on%20August%2017%20issued%20a%20press%20release%20that%20sought%20to%20fact-check%20media%20reports%20on%20the%20CAG%20report%E2%80%99s%20findings%20but%20did%20not%20cite%20a%20single%20specific%20example%20of%20the%20media%20falsely%20quoting%20the%20CAG%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F29145146%2Fabdm.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22894%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F29145146%2Fabdm.png%20894w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F29145146%2Fabdm-300x142.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-554936%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20illustration%20on%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Digital%20Mission%E2%80%99s%20official%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20other%20CAG%20reports%20found%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20these%20two%20reports%2C%20the%20ten%20other%20CAG%20reports%20also%20highlighted%20several%20other%20irregularities%20in%20Union%20government%20ministries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Toll%20Operations%20of%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20in%20Southern%20India%E2%80%99%20conducted%20on%2041%20randomly%20selected%20toll%20plazas%20across%20the%20five%20southern%20states%20found%20that%20in%20five%20toll%20plazas%2C%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%20132.05%20crore%20was%20collected%20from%20commuters%20in%20violation%20of%20toll%20plaza%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%20that%20the%20NHAI%20collected%20excess%20toll%20fees%20of%20Rs%2022.10%20crore%20from%20road%20users%20during%202017-2018%20to%202020-2021%20at%20the%20Paranur%20public-funded%20toll%20plaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20the%20regional%20connectivity%20scheme%20UDAN%20(Ude%20Desh%20Ka%20Aam%20Naagrik)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20found%20that%20up%20to%20March%202021%2C%20when%20UDAN-3%20ended%2C%2052%25%20(403%20out%20of%20774%20routes)%20of%20the%20awarded%20routes%20could%20not%20commence%20operations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20the%20financial%20audit%20of%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20found%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%20had%20incurred%20unsanctioned%20expenditure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202021-22%20financial%20year%20(FY)%2C%20the%20ministry%20had%20an%20unsanctioned%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2023%2C885.47%20crore%2C%20encompassing%201%2C937%20cases.%20In%20FY%202020-21%20unsanctioned%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%208%2C127.97%20crore%20was%20incurred%20by%20Indian%20Railways%20in%202%2C775%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98Departmental%20Trading%20Units%20Including%20Supply%20Chain%20Management%20in%20Khadi%20and%20Village%20Industries%20Commission%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20(MSME)%E2%80%99%20found%20that%20less%20than%2020%25%20of%20departmental%20trading%20units%20were%20operational.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20performance%20audit%20report%20of%20the%20Swadesh%20Darshan%20Scheme%20implemented%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%20said%20that%20while%20the%20scheme%20was%20launched%20with%20an%20initial%20outlay%20of%20Rs%20500%20crore%2C%20the%20ministry%20continued%20to%20sanction%20projects%20and%20the%20amount%20sanctioned%20had%20exceeded%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20by%202016-17.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98Role%20of%20Tea%20Board%20India%20in%20development%20of%20tea%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20recommended%20that%20the%20Tea%20Board%20initiate%20steps%20to%20investigate%20the%20cases%20of%20ineligible%20subsidy%20payments%20as%20these%20indicate%20%E2%80%9Ccorruption%2F%20fraud%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Compliance%20Audit%20on%20Finance%20and%20Communication%2C%20Union%20Government%E2%80%99%20contains%20significant%20findings%20from%20the%20compliance%20audit%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Communications%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Finance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20found%2C%20among%20others%2C%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Posts%20(DoP)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Communication%20did%20not%20formulate%20a%20conservation%20policy%20of%20its%20own%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20protection%20and%20conservation%20of%20Heritage%20Buildings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98Union%20Government%2C%20(Railways)%20Railways%20Finances%E2%80%99%20has%20revealed%20that%20Railways%20incurred%20an%20additional%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%207%2C778.43%20crore%20more%20than%20the%20sanctioned%20budget%20of%20Rs%205%2C7626.20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Performance%20Audit%20of%20the%20National%20Social%20Assistance%20Programme%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20Government%20(Civil)%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%E2%80%99%20found%20that%20funds%20meant%20to%20publicise%20the%20scheme%20were%20diverted%20for%20publicity%20of%20other%20schemes%20by%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20on%20the%20Union%20Government%20(Indirect%20Taxes%20%E2%80%93%20Customs)%20contains%20significant%20results%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20Audit%20of%20the%20Indian%20Customs%20Electronic%20Data%20Interchange%20System%20(ICES%201.5).%20The%20Audit%20said%20that%20the%20filing%20of%20custom%20duty%20refunds%20is%20being%20done%20manually%20and%20capturing%20and%20processing%20of%20refund%20claims%20needs%20to%20be%20automated%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20GSTN%20(Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20Network)%20System.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20read%20the%20major%20findings%20of%20all%20twelve%20CAG%20reports%20in%20a%20three-part%20series%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-nhai-toll-collection-railway-bharatmala-udan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-reports-government-corruption-tea-board-khadi-bsnl-swadesh-darshan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-on-indian-railways-expenses-ayushman-bharat-graft-diversion-of-pension-scheme-funds%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_BDqVanVhZo%3Fsi%3D17moKA6ZBKRnTl7g%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696991404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10231629%2Fgc-murmu.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fofficers-cag-reports-ayushman-bharat-bharatmala-transferred%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20reports%20put%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20on%20the%20backfoot%20after%20the%20opposition%20accused%20it%20of%20presiding%20over%20%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D%20in%20flagship%20schemes.%20The%20parties%20demanded%20accountability%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%22%2C%22aut