C%22%3EBack%20to%20their%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20were%20holed%20up%20in%20our%20homes%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20brainstormed%20ideas.%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20wholesome%20brand%20that%20helps%20people%20live%20a%20more%20sustainable%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Alankrutha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20research%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20start%20with%20clothing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20get%20skin%20allergies.%20When%20I%20wore%20certain%20clothes%2C%20I%20would%20get%20this%20red%20rash.%20I%20never%20took%20it%20very%20seriously%20as%20it%20would%20vanish%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20took%20a%20bath%20or%20removed%20the%20garment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-1-1696946463.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alankrutha%20moved%20back%20to%20India%20to%20start%20her%20sustainable%20business.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-1-1696946463.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-1-1696946463-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-1-1696946463-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-1-1696946463-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-1-1696946463-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331944%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAlankrutha%20moved%20back%20to%20India%20to%20start%20her%20sustainable%20business.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Alankrutha%20Chandra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%