ments.%20But%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20training%20or%20guidance%20in%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2053-year-old%20who%20grew%20up%20following%20Diego%20Armando%20Maradona%20%E2%80%94%20a%20professional%20football%20player%20from%20Argentina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tribal%20children%20grew%20up%20playing%20football%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20training.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20tribal%20children%20grew%20up%20playing%20football%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20training.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Raees%20was%20in%20Class%208%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20he%20played%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98under%2019%E2%80%99%20category%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20play%20football%20professionally%20at%20the%20national%20level%20seven%20times%20during%20his%20career.%20After%20graduating%20with%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Arts%20in%201995%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20job%20as%20a%20sports%20te