%20SMA%20Type-II%2C%20has%20been%20an%20exhausting%20process.%20With%20managing%20doctors%E2%80%99%20appointments%2C%20therapy%20and%20everything%20else%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20mother%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20days%20when%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%98why%20me%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20stigma%20of%20a%20genetic%20condition%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20our%20friends%20cut%20ties%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20festive%20celebration%2C%20Alpana%20recounts%2C%20a%20woman%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20her%20child%20eat%20the%20%3Cem%3Eprasad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(food%20offered%20to%20a%20deity)%20being%20distributed%20by%20Aarav%2C%20in%20fear%20of%20contacting%20SMA%20from%20him.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20one%20cannot%20pour%20from%20an%20empty%20cup%2C%20so%20I%20invested%20my%20energy%20and%20time%20in%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20abilities.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20helps%20both%20of%20us%20stay%20positive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlpana%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curesmaindia.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECure%20SMA%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20close-knit%20community%20of%20individuals%20with%20SMA%20and%20their%20caregivers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-2-1696514043.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-2-1696514043.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-2-1696514043-300x210.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-2-1696514043-500x349.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FS