%252Fnews%252Fzolgensma-the-world-s-most-expensive-drug-costs-rs-18-crore-per-dose-5-points-11615253464861.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20these%20costs%20are%20not%20covered%20under%20medical%20insurance%2C%20we%20often%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20crowdfunding%2C%20or%20in%20the%20worst%20case%20scenario%2C%20see%20a%20life%20slipping%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10104684%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D100%2525%2520of%2520the%2520patients%2520who%2Cdrug%2520for%2520SMA%2520Type%25201.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20shown%20that%20those%20who%20received%20the%20gene%20therapy%20treatment%20fared%20better%20in%20terms%20of%20survival%20rate%20and%20motor%20abilities.%20Patients%20who%20received%20the%20treatment%20early%20in%20life%20also%20showed%20the%20ability%20to%20even%20sit%20independently%20later%20in%20life.%20Since%20such%20treatments%20only%20help%20in%20preventing%20the%20condition%20from%20progressing%2C%20those%20who%20receive%20them%20require%20long-term%20rehabilitation%20support%20in%20the%20form%20of%20physiotherapy%2C%20which%20also%20adds%20to%20the%20costs%20of%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20exorbitant%20costs%20which%20make%20seeking%20treatment%20inaccessible%2C%20children%20with%20SMA%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20survival%20and%20often%20end%20up%20not%20making%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20continues.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20strong%20financial%20support%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20enhancing%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20886px)%20100vw%2C%20886px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_1835818411_11zon-1696514129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22886